      "seed": 827819487,
      "version": 320,
      "versionNonce": 232842815,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783366422551,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Goal: \"Services should be independently deployable\"\n- we can put a new version (or revert to an older version) ANY TIME WE WANT without coordination with other teams.\n- on the flip side, nothing another services deploys should break our side.\n- (This is 'Coupling')",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Goal: \"Services should be independently deployable\"\n- we can put a new version (or revert to an older version) ANY TIME WE WANT without coordination with other teams.\n- on the flip side, nothing another services deploys should break our side.\n- (This is 'Coupling')",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "hGqC_8qWFSO06XIryXj1x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 305,
      "y": 381,
      "width": 779.218994140625,
      "height": 243,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 232178385,
      "version": 286,
      "versionNonce": 1630539985,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783367357438,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Databases\n    - for DECADES, since the dawn of IT there was an idea of databases: SHARE THEM.\n    - \"Host based programming\" - Mainframe - all about. \n            - the \"business rules\" should live with the data (Stored procedures, etc.)\n\n\n\"Single point of failure!\"\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Databases\n    - for DECADES, since the dawn of IT there was an idea of databases: SHARE THEM.\n    - \"Host based programming\" - Mainframe - all about. \n            - the \"business rules\" should live with the data (Stored procedures, etc.)\n\n\n\"Single point of failure!\"\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
