      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783367158772,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- We don't break, we slow WAYYY down.\n- Process\n    - \"Data Architects\" - a whole layer of management that is the gate keeper\n    - Lots of coordination\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- We don't break, we slow WAYYY down.\n- Process\n    - \"Data Architects\" - a whole layer of management that is the gate keeper\n    - Lots of coordination\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "8Jd78b10aLvBChMQEAgTV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 606,
      "y": 1226,
      "width": 763.2189331054688,
      "height": 54,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 867936081,
      "version": 174,
      "versionNonce": 43474865,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783367250187,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "if you have to do all that work, you don't do it. You create \"hacks\", work-arounds, etc.\n(maybe we can cram the data we need in the same column as other data, etc.)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "if you have to do all that work, you don't do it. You create \"hacks\", work-arounds, etc.\n(maybe we can cram the data we need in the same column as other data, etc.)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "zDFUdrGXRWa4UVJwr6gBb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 214,
      "y": 938,
      "width": 474.2193298339844,
      "height": 27,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
