      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783367361016,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Our team's repostory. Deployed and tested as a unit.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Our team's repostory. Deployed and tested as a unit.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "69Wm7uIVQ-g-2V8VoNRnm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 230,
      "y": 1334,
      "width": 992.1185302734375,
      "height": 270,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1088164351,
      "version": 421,
      "versionNonce": 1734925425,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783367808933,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Microservice - mostly from Netflix. \n\n\"What does 'Micro'\" mean - size? what unit of measure?\n\n- \"Small enough to fit in your head\"\n    - You and your team understand the domain, the code, etc.\n\nMicroservices are two weeks big. \"Disposable Code\" \n    - This is actually really good and valuable in *many* ways - and maybe more so again now that we have AI.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Microservice - mostly from Netflix. \n\n\"What does 'Micro'\" mean - size? what unit of measure?\n\n- \"Small enough to fit in your head\"\n    - You and your team understand the domain, the code, etc.\n\nMicroservices are two weeks big. \"Disposable Code\" \n    - This is actually really good and valuable in *many* ways - and maybe more so again now that we have AI.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
